    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Mocks"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Mocks for all modules shall be kept in a centralized repo (cnconvbase/autosar/mocks)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Each module can create a folder for their mocks. With this we can reuse Mock function of a certain module in all module Unit tst"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Please don't create mocks inside module Unit test folder. Mocks should be in centralized repo as mentioned above"
    },
